{"tid":981430,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"To Z","createTime":"2019-01-14T09:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T12:36:47.000Z","uid":56088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c1af8b245936e1a31350107292ba0faee736f1b","tid":981430,"uid":56088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"以前，我嘅責任係哄你開心，陪住你<br />\n<br />\n宜家，我只可以控制住自己唔再搵你，煩你，<br />\n<br />\n雖然最尾你都係block哂我啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我只係想話你知，如果我一早知道你仲想同我見面，<br />\n<br />\n我根本唔會做埋啲咁不智嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我真系忍得好辛苦，忍到自己食唔安坐唔落<br />\n<br />\n去到最尾，誤會愈來愈多，我知你亦唔會聽我解釋<br />\n<br />\n由頭到尾我只係想知你到底諗緊啲乜<br />\n<br />\n係，我認我系一個唔識拍拖嘅人，<br />\n<br />\n好多野都因為衝動而做錯，講錯左野<br />\n<br />\n但係由始至終，除左個陣呃你訓左教，其實去左打波之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係冇呃過你，我只系唔識包裝自己，<br />\n<br />\n俾你見到我最差個一面<br />\n<br />\n我知已經返唔到轉頭，<br />\n<br />\n我知你會話我上連登開post好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我真係冇哂方法去搵你，我先咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n希望你睇到，當俾多次機會我解釋又好<br />\n<br />\n睇完當笑下都好<br />\n<br />\n希望你以後開開心心咁過日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85b6b8c2470c7f05b0db86c4dbf83e66ff12b34","tid":981430,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4902509207c0bd36e1959a37f7c202741730b8d9","tid":981430,"uid":82466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"扮大方 真係好撚肉酸"},{"pid":"12ad2d05b0d5fe48b5cf2e0b9904f6af0f0e19ca","tid":981430,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85b6b8c2470c7f05b0db86c4dbf83e66ff12b34","tid":981430,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets